    "description": "<strong>THIS ROSE-TINTED ZIGGURAT</strong><br>Set in the modern day suburbs, a quiet neighborhood awakes to the sound of leaves, vehicles and falling tears.<br>Follow the trials of an unnamed woman in this horror &amp; life-simulator hybrid as she attempts to pack away years of memorabilia, built with her family that now seems absent from her life and from this <u>house</u>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289490/extras/7edcef14b8a0e5de7a99483481f1a636.poster.avif?t=1675333944\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289490/extras/7edcef14b8a0e5de7a99483481f1a636.webm?t=1675333944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289490/extras/7edcef14b8a0e5de7a99483481f1a636.mp4?t=1675333944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>TILE, WOOD, LINEOLEUM.</strong><br>Experience comfort as well as fear in this narrative-driven horror about time, memory and the cost of nostalgia.<br>A Lovecraftian tale inspired by the works of Mark Z. Danielewski, Junji Ito and Charlie Kaufman.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289490/extras/e4b63a0cd7f10c8ef51a71db0066f7b5.poster.avif?t=1675333944\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289490/extras/e4b63a0cd7f10c8ef51a71db0066f7b5.webm?t=1675333944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289490/extras/e4b63a0cd7f10c8ef51a71db0066f7b5.mp4?t=1675333944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>FAMILIAR FACES AND EMPTY ROOMS</strong><br>Explore and excavate the memories that stain the walls of this <u>house</u>, as the environment itself shifts and struggles with you and against you.<br>But watch your step, the entities that hold this <u>house</u> dear may not approve of your attempted departure. <br>Call upon relics of bygone love to hold this <u>house</u> together, keep yourself together and make it to the morning.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289490/extras/7e87010a6857b2a5026c0641858707f5.poster.avif?t=1675333944\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289490/extras/7e87010a6857b2a5026c0641858707f5.webm?t=1675333944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289490/extras/7e87010a6857b2a5026c0641858707f5.mp4?t=1675333944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
